Malaysia’s Kurnia Asia May Sell Insurance Unit, Edge Reports

-- B y   C h o n g   P o o i   K o o n
-- 
2011-07-16T02:28:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-16/malaysia-s-kurnia-asia-may-sell-insurance-unit-edge-reports.html
Malaysia’s  Kurnia Asia Bhd. (KUAB)  is
seeking to sell its insurance unit to cut debt, the Edge
newspaper reported, citing people it didn’t identify.  The sale has attracted several bidders, the report said
without naming the potential buyers. Company officials couldn’t
be reached by the Edge for comment, the report said.  To contact the reporter for this story:
Chong Pooi Koon in  Kuala Lumpur  at 
 pchong17@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Tighe at 
 ptighe@bloomberg.net  